Class ZipFile.CompositeZipEntrySource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.sawdust.io.ZipFile.CompositeZipEntrySource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ZipFile.ZipEntrySource, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    ZipFile

    public static class ZipFile.CompositeZipEntrySource
extends java.lang.Object
implements ZipFile.ZipEntrySource
    The CompositeZipEntrySource provides a zip entry source made from a series of ZipEntrySources. This class can be used to condense mulitple data sources into a singe zip entry source.
